SysReq_1:
The system must have a watchdog timer (IWDG) which is triggerd within 1 second. If one second passes without the reset of the IWDG, a reset should be performed.
(Stake_Req_1)

SysReq_2:
The system must have a USART module which is capable of sending data out to another controller. 
(Stake_Req_2)

SysReq_3:
The system must have a USART module which is capable of receiving data from another controller. 
(Stake_Req_2)

SysReq_4:
The system must have a SPI module which is capable of sending data out to another controller.
(Stake_Req_2)

SysReq_5:
The system must have a SPI module which is capable of receiving data from another controller. 
(Stake_Req_2)

SysReq_6:
The system must implement a function to read out the data of a DHT11 sensor. 
(Stake_Req_3)

SysReq_7:
The system must convert and interprete the temperature data. 
(Stake_Req_4)

SysReq_8:
The system must convert and interprete the humidity data. 
(Stake_Req_5)

SysReq_9:
The system must connect the interpretation of the data to the LED on the board.
(Stake_Req_4)(Stake_Req_5)

SysReq_10:
The system must read out the data of the DHT11 sensor every second.
(Stake_Req_6)

SysReq_11:
The system must have a OLED display which is connected with the controller. 
(Stake_Req_7)

SysReq_12:
The system must have a function to display error/warning information on the display. 
(Stake_Req_7)

SysReq_13:
The system must have a function to display the temperature and humidity information on the display. 
(Stake_Req_8)
